        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 31 at 12:08AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 1208 AM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Lutie, or 9 miles north of Wellington, moving south at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Wellington, Quail, and Lutie.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
